7745", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569458_2180220805711078_8464685874959413905_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WLwFc6L1ERYQ7kNvgHzojw1&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDSy48XW9JirLmORv-plV4tPOLS49OnFs5zTGlgzgpsWg&oe=6701196B"}, {"file_name": "GeoVoyageScreen1.png", "id": "1260872674929494", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974611_1260872678262827_3662430706508410666_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=HAp93ldvD60Q7kNvgGIkTj7&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBJgz491ge0HcpJ0ClFrRreg_s0auw01mkhsTEnaTKKIw&oe=67010DA6"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Geo Voyage", "keywords": ["Education", "Travel", "Exploration", "Globe", "Earth"], "long_description": "Geo Voyage invites you on an extraordinary journey around the globe. With a visually stunning 3D globe and interactive features, this app brings the world to your fingertips.\n\nExplore the Globe: Spin the globe to reveal famous landmarks and wonders worldwide. Tap any location to learn exciting facts and dive into immersive experiences. Street view maps and panoramic photos transport you to the heart of your chosen destination, allowing you to explore as if you were there.\n\nGeo Voyage AI: Have questions about the world? Geo Voyage\u2019s AI companion will tell you what you want to know about geography, culture, and more. Ask Earth your question and reveal an exciting new way to learn.\n\nDaily Challenges and Global Headlines: Stay up-to-date with the latest news and engage in daily challenges that test your world knowledge. Learn about different cultures, historical events, and current affairs while exploring the globe.\n\nDiscover the World: Whether you\u2019re a curious traveler, a history enthusiast, or simply looking for a new way to explore our planet, Geo Voyage offers a unique and engaging experience. Download now and embark on your global adventure!", "s